1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:04,000
{\an8}<b><font color="#9CD5FF">One Pace Premium</font></b>
Keep the project alive: <font color="#a8c7fa">ko-fi.com/not6ip</font>

2
00:01:41,910 --> 00:01:44,410
Wano's Grand Sumo Tournament

3
00:01:44,410 --> 00:01:46,620
That's a huge lion-dog!

4
00:01:46,620 --> 00:01:48,300
Whose is it?

5
00:01:49,210 --> 00:01:52,500
How do we find this Otama kid?

6
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:56,420
The townsfolk wouldn't tell us
even if we asked.

7
00:01:56,420 --> 00:02:00,530
They're all under Orochi's influence.

8
00:02:02,170 --> 00:02:06,230
But some of them look like
ordinary people, not fighters.

9
00:02:07,370 --> 00:02:10,220
There have always been regular villagers here.

10
00:02:10,910 --> 00:02:16,230
Until twenty years ago,
this was a vibrant castle town.

11
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:21,820
But one day, Orochi's subordinates came
and seized the houses they desired.

12
00:02:22,570 --> 00:02:24,790
Then, except for essential merchants...

13
00:02:26,390 --> 00:02:30,840
everyone was expelled from town.

14
00:02:32,770 --> 00:02:36,260
That's the story behind Bakura Town.

15
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:03,780
A sumo wrestler? How did he...?

16
00:03:05,780 --> 00:03:08,200
Something's going on further into town.

17
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:10,670
Since a sumo wrestler came flying out...

18
00:03:10,670 --> 00:03:12,330
I suppose it's a sumo match.

19
00:03:18,450 --> 00:03:23,800
Once again, is there no one
who can take down...

20
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:30,130
the yokozuna of the
Flower Capital, Urashima?!

21
00:03:26,220 --> 00:03:31,140
Urashima

22
00:03:38,390 --> 00:03:40,760
Another bunch of weaklings.

23
00:03:48,770 --> 00:03:49,700
There're more.

24
00:03:58,950 --> 00:04:02,260
Sumo, huh? Sounds fun!

25
00:04:08,370 --> 00:04:14,810
Urashima so far has fought
and bested nineteen wrestlers.

26
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:20,150
But when it comes to the number of
bones broken, there have been...

27
00:04:21,630 --> 00:04:23,850
Ten arm bones...

28
00:04:23,850 --> 00:04:26,100
fifteen leg bones...

29
00:04:26,100 --> 00:04:28,370
fifty-two ribs...

30
00:04:28,370 --> 00:04:30,830
four skulls, and...

31
00:04:30,830 --> 00:04:33,610
seven backbones!

32
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:39,500
That's eighty-eight bones in total,
and four wrestlers are missing!

33
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:42,920
Overwhelming!

34
00:04:43,530 --> 00:04:47,140
His strength is inhuman!

35
00:04:47,140 --> 00:04:49,500
The undefeated monster!

36
00:04:49,500 --> 00:04:55,900
Yokozuna Urashima!

37
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:59,980
Today, we have a special exhibition match!

38
00:05:00,070 --> 00:05:03,490
He who defeats Urashima takes home
a staggering 500 gold coins!

39
00:05:04,090 --> 00:05:06,110
Take down Urashima!

40
00:05:06,110 --> 00:05:07,910
I'll bet on you!

41
00:05:07,910 --> 00:05:10,320
You can do it, guys!

42
00:05:11,390 --> 00:05:15,120
We have the perfect plan!
We'll win the prize!

43
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:17,650
Beat those jerks!

44
00:05:17,650 --> 00:05:19,540
Lord Urashima!

45
00:05:26,220 --> 00:05:29,140
Oh! Look at this!

46
00:05:33,550 --> 00:05:35,180
Ready...

47
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:38,400
Go!

48
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:50,490
Okiku!

49
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:56,330
I knew you would come!

50
00:05:57,830 --> 00:06:02,040
This means you've decided
to be my wife, right?!

51
00:06:05,190 --> 00:06:06,960
Excuse me.

52
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:09,300
You won't be able to hide behind me.

53
00:06:09,300 --> 00:06:12,120
I can't believe it!

54
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:16,810
This woman is engaged to Urashima?!

55
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:22,770
How lucky! She's loved by a yokozuna!

56
00:06:22,770 --> 00:06:28,670
This is one hell of a scandal!

57
00:06:28,670 --> 00:06:32,390
What?! The great Urashima has a wife?!

58
00:06:32,390 --> 00:06:33,690
His wife?

59
00:06:33,690 --> 00:06:34,790
No...

60
00:06:36,930 --> 00:06:42,750
As you saw earlier, his belief
is that I will marry him.

61
00:06:45,370 --> 00:06:50,020
Okiku! I have a match in Bakura Town later!

62
00:06:50,020 --> 00:06:54,010
If you're interested,
come and see how strong I am!

63
00:06:59,150 --> 00:07:02,480
My interests do not align with his.

64
00:07:04,910 --> 00:07:06,360
I see.

65
00:07:07,450 --> 00:07:09,490
You guys!

66
00:07:09,490 --> 00:07:12,450
We're looking for someone!

67
00:07:12,450 --> 00:07:15,160
She's a little girl named Tama!

68
00:07:15,730 --> 00:07:18,870
Tell me where this town's boss is!

69
00:07:18,870 --> 00:07:21,010
She should be there!

70
00:07:22,610 --> 00:07:27,340
That woman is so frustrating!
Damn gold digger...!

71
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:31,830
She's huge, but that's perfect for Urashima!

72
00:07:31,830 --> 00:07:34,300
I'd be a better match!

73
00:07:35,450 --> 00:07:37,010
They're not listening...

74
00:07:37,010 --> 00:07:42,480
Okiku came to see me. Guys, bring her to me!

75
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,650
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

76
00:07:43,650 --> 00:07:46,940
Big Bro! I didn't know you were such a player!

77
00:07:46,940 --> 00:07:50,240
Everyone wants to be like you!
No wonder she fell for you!

78
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:53,360
Okiku!

79
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:57,280
Okay, we're gonna look
for her ourselves! Let's go!

80
00:07:59,870 --> 00:08:03,960
Hey, lady! Big Bro Urashima wants
to see you! Come with us!

81
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:06,460
Out of our way, jerks!

82
00:08:06,460 --> 00:08:08,250
Kick their asses!

83
00:08:10,460 --> 00:08:12,430
Don't get in our way!

84
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:32,400
What?!

85
00:08:32,950 --> 00:08:34,740
Nice charge!

86
00:08:40,380 --> 00:08:43,510
I guess the winning technique
was a frontal thrust.

87
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:47,520
Come with me, lady!

88
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:49,380
No... Please stop!

89
00:08:53,170 --> 00:08:57,140
Would you really slash
an unarmed naked man?

90
00:09:04,020 --> 00:09:06,810
Yahoo!

91
00:09:08,650 --> 00:09:12,610
Heave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho!

92
00:09:14,570 --> 00:09:16,070
Kiku!

93
00:09:18,780 --> 00:09:20,200
Outta my way!

94
00:09:28,580 --> 00:09:31,340
Hey, Zoro! Why did you
let them take her away?!

95
00:09:36,590 --> 00:09:37,720
I'm sorry...

96
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:41,140
I thought that it wasn't right...

97
00:09:41,870 --> 00:09:43,680
to slash a naked man.

98
00:09:44,650 --> 00:09:45,820
Besides...

99
00:09:46,810 --> 00:09:50,190
she's not just a teahouse waitress.

100
00:09:53,310 --> 00:09:56,570
Hey! Isn't she a girl from
the teahouse in the other town?!

101
00:09:56,570 --> 00:10:01,240
With her rank, it's presumptuous
of her to even enter this town!

102
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:05,450
Is that so?! Then we've gotta kick her out!

103
00:10:05,450 --> 00:10:07,670
She's a vulgar tramp!

104
00:10:10,540 --> 00:10:13,500
Shut up, you commoners!

105
00:10:17,220 --> 00:10:23,460
To us samurai, every one of you fools is
the same, vulgar, second-class citizen!

106
00:10:26,290 --> 00:10:29,100
Your lives are worthless!

107
00:10:29,100 --> 00:10:31,940
It's up to me...

108
00:10:33,190 --> 00:10:35,400
whether you live or die!

109
00:10:56,830 --> 00:11:01,850
So, Okiku!

110
00:11:01,850 --> 00:11:03,640
Why don't you...

111
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:05,760
be...

112
00:11:06,300 --> 00:11:09,640
mine?!

113
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:18,370
This humble servant doesn't
know a single citizen...

114
00:11:19,210 --> 00:11:20,650
who is second class!

115
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:53,210
Enough of your jokes!

116
00:11:53,860 --> 00:11:56,440
The only vulgar thing here is your heart.

117
00:12:06,620 --> 00:12:09,410
The yokozuna's topknot!

118
00:12:15,040 --> 00:12:18,260
So cool!

119
00:12:18,260 --> 00:12:21,420
Kiku's got guts!

120
00:12:21,420 --> 00:12:24,330
It's getting exciting now!

121
00:12:26,010 --> 00:12:28,930
He got rejected by that woman...

122
00:12:28,930 --> 00:12:31,890
and got his topknot chopped off!

123
00:12:31,890 --> 00:12:34,520
That should get their boss out here quickly.

124
00:12:50,830 --> 00:12:55,170
Okiku!

125
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:58,000
You...

126
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:00,960
betrayed me!

127
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:05,590
How could I do that...

128
00:13:06,580 --> 00:13:07,890
in front of others?!

129
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:14,250
He looks like a wrathful deity!

130
00:13:19,210 --> 00:13:20,860
Okiku!

131
00:13:21,730 --> 00:13:24,190
Oh no! That pose is...

132
00:13:24,190 --> 00:13:27,070
...his Transcendent Slap
that sends opponents flying!

133
00:13:28,180 --> 00:13:30,660
Please forgive me, Lord Urashima!

134
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:38,000
However...

135
00:13:41,450 --> 00:13:46,010
It seems that you truly are
the kind of man who would hit a woman.

136
00:13:50,760 --> 00:13:53,930
Die!

137
00:14:14,450 --> 00:14:17,290
Gum-Gum...

138
00:14:18,420 --> 00:14:19,710
Sumo Slap!

139
00:14:50,680 --> 00:14:54,240
Wh-Wh-Whoa, whoa, whoa... Uh-oh, uh-oh, uh-oh...!

140
00:14:55,580 --> 00:14:56,630
No, no, no!

141
00:14:57,710 --> 00:14:58,540
Oh no, oh no!

142
00:15:15,180 --> 00:15:17,680
Damn!

143
00:15:18,750 --> 00:15:21,730
What did you do to my slap?!

144
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:28,190
Damn you... Who are you to Okiku?!

145
00:15:28,190 --> 00:15:32,320
Get out of my way!

146
00:15:32,900 --> 00:15:36,700
I have to tear Okiku into bits...

147
00:15:37,250 --> 00:15:40,000
Otherwise I'll lose face!

148
00:15:40,950 --> 00:15:42,790
Okay! No problem!

149
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:44,850
That is...

150
00:15:45,670 --> 00:15:47,680
Dosukoi!

151
00:15:48,750 --> 00:15:50,050
Dosukoi!

152
00:15:54,390 --> 00:15:56,480
If you can beat me!

153
00:15:59,220 --> 00:16:00,060
I'm...

154
00:16:02,330 --> 00:16:04,900
good at sumo!

155
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:09,820
Luffy-no-umi

156
00:16:09,820 --> 00:16:12,200
Get...

157
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:14,410
out of my way!

158
00:16:14,410 --> 00:16:17,580
Bodhisattva Slap!

159
00:16:31,370 --> 00:16:34,010
He's dodging Urashima's slaps!

160
00:16:34,010 --> 00:16:35,760
He's so agile!

161
00:16:36,860 --> 00:16:38,430
Get serious, kiddo!

162
00:16:38,430 --> 00:16:41,020
You can't win by just dodging!

163
00:16:52,570 --> 00:16:54,480
Ear Smasher!

164
00:16:56,590 --> 00:16:57,240
Hey!

165
00:16:57,240 --> 00:16:58,280
Eye Gouger!

166
00:17:04,820 --> 00:17:08,380
Hey! Those are all illegal moves!

167
00:17:08,380 --> 00:17:10,560
Shut up!

168
00:17:11,550 --> 00:17:13,670
I'm...

169
00:17:13,670 --> 00:17:18,800
a yokozuna!

170
00:17:22,410 --> 00:17:24,800
Well, whatever!

171
00:17:28,770 --> 00:17:31,230
Boss Holdem! We have a problem!

172
00:17:31,230 --> 00:17:36,150
Huh? The yokozuna got his topknot
chopped off by a woman?

173
00:17:36,150 --> 00:17:40,700
Everyone's upset!
And we don't know what to do!

174
00:17:40,700 --> 00:17:44,870
I don't care! What do you expect me to do?!

175
00:17:51,700 --> 00:17:56,720
I'm busy tearing her cheek off!

176
00:17:58,840 --> 00:18:03,350
Leave me alone! You can
have your baboon back!

177
00:18:03,350 --> 00:18:06,230
Please stop!

178
00:18:07,390 --> 00:18:09,710
Not a chance!

179
00:18:10,620 --> 00:18:15,880
I was told you mentioned the name "Kozuki."

180
00:18:19,450 --> 00:18:24,700
When the Kozuki Clan comes back,
they'll teach you a lesson!

181
00:18:25,970 --> 00:18:28,650
You must be aware...

182
00:18:29,670 --> 00:18:33,270
that saying the name "Kozuki"...

183
00:18:33,270 --> 00:18:35,420
is a serious crime!

184
00:18:36,350 --> 00:18:40,720
So this doubles as your punishment.

185
00:18:42,520 --> 00:18:46,280
You should've stopped chasing ghosts.

186
00:18:46,280 --> 00:18:49,360
The Kozuki were an evil clan...

187
00:18:49,810 --> 00:18:57,170
that tried to destroy Wano twenty years ago!

188
00:19:17,050 --> 00:19:19,170
Move it, punk!

189
00:19:20,140 --> 00:19:24,720
There's no fixing what Okiku has done!

190
00:19:26,520 --> 00:19:31,740
She turned down the honor of
marrying and serving me, a samurai...

191
00:19:33,100 --> 00:19:34,900
and tarnished my good name!

192
00:19:35,770 --> 00:19:40,080
I'll smash her brains in to set an example!

193
00:19:54,410 --> 00:19:56,250
Just shut up!

194
00:19:56,250 --> 00:19:58,670
Like I said, do as you like once you beat me!

195
00:20:12,190 --> 00:20:14,940
You can't beat me though!

196
00:20:17,400 --> 00:20:18,650
What do you mean?!

197
00:20:20,350 --> 00:20:21,820
I'm...

198
00:20:23,040 --> 00:20:25,450
I'm...

199
00:20:25,500 --> 00:20:31,540
the greatest yokozuna in Wano!

200
00:20:33,250 --> 00:20:35,790
Transcendent Slap!

201
00:20:52,350 --> 00:20:54,400
What's this?

202
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:56,350
I don't know. What could it be?

203
00:21:10,930 --> 00:21:13,250
You may be a yokozuna...

204
00:21:16,410 --> 00:21:17,250
but I'm...

205
00:21:21,630 --> 00:21:25,480
the man who's gonna be King of the Pirates!

206
00:21:29,890 --> 00:21:31,560
Ow, ow, ow, ow...

207
00:21:32,660 --> 00:21:36,230
Big Bro Luffy!

208
00:21:36,650 --> 00:21:39,320
Gum-Gum...

209
00:22:01,340 --> 00:22:03,300
Gigant...

210
00:22:04,880 --> 00:22:08,970
Sumo Slap!

211
00:22:28,150 --> 00:22:32,450
Dosukoi

212
00:22:52,600 --> 00:22:54,430
No...!

213
00:22:56,670 --> 00:22:57,770
What the...?

214
00:23:37,400 --> 00:23:40,510
A-Am I safe now?

215
00:23:53,100 --> 00:23:55,960
Th-The yokozuna...

216
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:59,990
was sent flying!

217
00:24:00,370 --> 00:24:02,790
Yokozuna!

218
00:24:02,790 --> 00:24:06,750
No way! He couldn't have lost
to a little guy like him!

219
00:24:16,360 --> 00:24:19,310
That makes me the yokozuna!

220
00:24:19,310 --> 00:24:23,810
I don't care who you are,
just bring it on!

221
00:24:26,920 --> 00:24:30,030
I guess we did enough to
get the attention of their boss.

222
00:24:31,060 --> 00:24:32,070
I think so!

223
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:35,030
Th-That guy...

224
00:24:35,560 --> 00:24:38,990
I remember! He's that magistrate killer...!

225
00:24:42,000 --> 00:24:43,920
Zorojuro?!

226
00:24:52,100 --> 00:24:53,930
So what?

227
00:25:00,120 --> 00:25:03,330
Don't tell me he's that guy's ally!

228
00:25:07,270 --> 00:25:08,480
Hey!

229
00:25:09,910 --> 00:25:12,440
Bring the boss of this town!

230
00:25:36,380 --> 00:25:38,720
We're here to take back Tama!
